      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This example exhibits excellent compression across all cylinders and has received a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and valve shim adjustment within the last 5,000 miles. The chassis is structurally sound with documented rear subframe reinforcement already completed, mitigating the platform's primary fatigue point. Performance is bolstered by a factory variable M-differential lock and MacPherson strut front/multi-link rear suspension that maintains tight damping characteristics. While the paint displays minor road-rash consistent with its mileage, the powertrain remains in peak operating condition, delivering a linear power band and the iconic metallic rasp of the individual throttle bodies. This is a driver-focused machine ready for immediate engagement.",
